{"tid":1261389,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛技巧你要知！","createTime":"2019-06-27T08:13:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T18:52:47.000Z","uid":259820,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"507b3122fcec6211fe7cf6197f3d0bde6dc353cd","tid":1261389,"uid":259820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:13:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BA%94%E6%AF%9B%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7%E4%BD%A0%E8%A6%81%E7%9F%A5/?fbclid=IwAR2BB8pKsi-lnjFfMdxtJIXYz6Rkh7C9repIjHzSaPt8waOeAuIf8nskk6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%25AF%259B%25E6%258A%2580%25E5%25B7%25A7%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%259F%25A5%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2BB8pKsi-lnjFfMdxtJIXYz6Rkh7C9repIjHzSaPt8waOeAuIf8nskk6g&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0djX0Nqj3uEASyejP0bzfnYY%3D&h=5a6a9d80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%25AF%259B%25E6%258A%2580%25E5%25B7%25A7%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%259F%25A5%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2BB8pKsi-lnjFfMdxtJIXYz6Rkh7C9repIjHzSaPt8waOeAuIf8nskk6g&h=c053c22d\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BA%94%E6%AF%9B%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7%E4%BD%A0%E8%A6%81%E7%9F%A5/?fbclid=IwAR2BB8pKsi-lnjFfMdxtJIXYz6Rkh7C9repIjHzSaPt8waOeAuIf8nskk6g</a><br />\n<br />\n用 2014 的經驗，政府、差佬後退之後，港共、中共並唔會放軟手腳，而係轉而用文宣系統全面反擊。愛港力之類你當然一早知啦。但就算係討論區如連登，都有可能被滲透。呢個時候就要小心，唔好比人帶走高質的連登討論。<br />\n<br />\n以下係曾經外流的五毛手冊內容，其中第 8 點尤其重要！<br />\n<br />\n6、必要时可以制造更加耸人听闻的假新闻，吸引网民视线，然后很快澄清该消息纯属谣言。<br />\n<br />\n7、某些论坛人气不错，网友信用度比较高，这时首先要做的是制造一种混乱，通过似是而非的文章进行干涉，跟贴作非理性的故意曲解、制造误会和争辩，转移网民注意力。<br />\n<br />\n8、海外网站较难控制，当不能主导论坛舆论的时候，可以采用大量短贴、无实质内容贴、非理性贴进行刷屏，令版面充斥无意义的混乱，使读者失去兴趣，这样达到避免反动思想流通传播的目的。<br />\n<br />\n連登而家咁勁，當然冇可能被中共改變思想風向。但用第8點，就係用無意義的內容去充斥，令D人花時間去講D無謂野洗版。咁就足以破壞「反動思想」的傳播，甚至破壞一個討論區的團結同互信。<br />\n<br />\n早前係連登上出現攻擊「左膠」的文宣。我個人希望係少數真心憎恨左膠的人士所為。但萬一，五毛用呢種對左膠的憎恨，去開 po，充斥連登，咁就好可怕。<br />\n<br />\n憎左膠，有舊怨，我明白。但而家左膠的影響力為零的當下去提左膠，就令人覺得係別有用心。花時間討論點提防已不存在的左膠，以後個個 po 都問下係咪想左膠散水，咁成個討論氣氛亦會急速惡化。<br />\n<br />\n防範的方法好簡單，一，factcheck；二，問當下的討論有冇意義，係咪為運動好。有呢兩個原則，好快就知攻擊左膠po係好無作用，最後其怪自敗。<br />\n<br />\n參考：五毛手冊: <a href=\"https://chineselawstudent.wordpress.com/2011/04/15/%E4%BA%94%E6%AF%9B%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%89%8B%E5%86%8C-%E3%80%8A%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E3%80%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchineselawstudent.wordpress.com%2F2011%2F04%2F15%2F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%25AF%259B%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%2586%258C-%25E3%2580%258A%25E7%25BD%2591%25E7%25BB%259C%25E8%25AF%2584%25E8%25AE%25BA%25E5%2591%2598%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258D%2597%25E3%2580%258B%2F&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0djX0Nqj3uEASyejP0bzfnYY%3D&h=7794178f\" target=\"_blank\">https://chineselawstudent.wordpress.com/2011/04/15/%E4%BA%94%E6%AF%9B%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%89%8B%E5%86%8C-%E3%80%8A%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E3%80%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\nShare from 立場新聞，大家可以睇睇﹗"},{"pid":"5eaefbb08e515f24c9c47f3f8e09ad18f42908ef","tid":1261389,"uid":86985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:14:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c9d2072d68dae534cd3ae32eed6001cdd94aaa4","tid":1261389,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:15:41.000Z","msg":"推上去比人睇下"},{"pid":"70a9de59cce258a241965830d5ad0338293d8d5a","tid":1261389,"uid":259820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:15:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a5dc704b691ade4a3532ac4b4487b91d7f7d135e","tid":1261389,"uid":259820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e6ed679ac79237ae629031f650a06fb8482c55","tid":1261389,"uid":259820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"